}}},"widgets_values":["Увеличьте shift, если вы получаете слишком много размытых / темных / плохих изображений. Уменьшите, если вы хотите увеличить детализацию."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":95,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-130,-220],"size":[490,180],"flags":{},"order":8,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Custom Nodes","properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["## ✔ Custom Nodes, которые нужно установить в Manager  \n\n- **ControlAltAI_Nodes**\n- **ComfyUI-Easy-Use**\n- **rgthree-comfy**\n- **ComfyUI-GGUF**\n"],"color":"#322","bgcolor":"#533"},{"id":67,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-540,10],"size":[540,800],"flags":{},"order":9,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"Model links","properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["[ComfyUI Туториал](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/image/qwen/qwen-image)\n\n\n## Ссылки на модели\n\nВы можете найти модели на [Huggingface](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/tree/main) или [Modelscope](https://modelscope.cn/models/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/files)\n\n**Diffusion model**\n\n- [qwen_image_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/qwen_image_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors)\n\n**Qwen_image_distill**\n\n- [qwen_image_distill_full_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/non_official/diffusion_models/qwen_image_distill_full_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors)\n- [qwen_image_distill_full_bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/non_official/diffusion_models/qwen_image_distill_full_bf16.safetensors)\n\n**GGUF model (Q4, Q8 - на ваш выбор)**\n\n- [city96/Qwen-Image-gguf](https://huggingface.co/city96/Qwen-Image-gguf/tree/main)\n\n**LoRA (на выбор, в зависимости от шагов)**\n\n- [Qwen-Image-Lightning-4steps-V1.0.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Qwen-Image-Lightning/resolve/main/Qwen-Image-Lightning-4steps-V1.0.safetensors?download=true)\n- [Qwen-Image-Lightning-8steps-V1.0.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/lightx2v/Qwen-Image-Lightning/resolve/main/Qwen-Image-Lightning-8steps-V1.0.safetensors)\n\n**Text encoder**\n\n- [qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors)\n\n**Text encoder GGUF (опционально, на выбор)**\n\n- [Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct-GGUF](https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Qwen2.5-VL-7B-Instruct-GGUF/tree/main)\n\n**VAE**\n\n- [qwen_image_vae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors)\n\nModel Storage Location\n\n```\n📂 ComfyUI/\n├── 📂 models/\n│   ├── 📂 diffusion_models/\n│   │   ├── qwen_image_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n│   │   └── qwen_image_distill_full_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n│   ├── 📂 loras/\n│   │   └── Qwen-Image-Lightning-8steps-V1.0.safetensors\n│   ├── 📂 vae/\n│   │   └── qwen_image_vae.safetensors\n│   └── 📂 text_encoders/\n│       └── qwen_2.5_vl_7b_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n```\n\n## 🎈 Upscale Model  \n\n### Скачать 4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth mode from [ТУТ](https://huggingface.co/uwg/upscaler/resolve/main/ESRGAN/4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth?download=true)  \n\n**Положить:** `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models`\n\n---\n\n## 📚 Resources  \n🎥 **Видео по Qwen ComfyUI:** [Егор Смышников YT](https://youtu.be/kR6gQ7GRWEI)  \n\n💬 **Сообщество Гильдия: Генеративный:** [Присоединиться](https://t.me/tribute/app?startapp=sgyZ)"],"color":"#233","bgcolor":"#355"},{"id":70,"type":"Note","pos":[1180,690],"size":[320,140],"flags":{},"order":10,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"For fp8 without 8steps LoRA","properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["Установите значение cfg равным 1.0, чтобы повысить скорость за счет согласованности. Такие сэмплеры, как res_multistep, довольно хорошо работают с cfg 1.0\n\nОфициальное количество шагов равно 50, но я думаю, что это слишком много. Кажется, что даже всего 10 шагов работают."],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":99,"type":"UnetLoaderGGUF","pos":[20,60],"size":[330,60],"flags":{},"order":11,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"unet_name","name":"unet_name","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"unet_name"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"MODEL","name":"MODEL","type":"MODEL","links":[159]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-gguf","ver":"1.1.3","Node name for S&R":"UnetLoaderGGUF","ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{"unet_name":true}}},"widgets_values":["qwen-image-Q4_0.gguf"]},{"id":74,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[855.4173583984375,691.4207763671875],"size":[300,280],"flags":{},"order":12,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"KSampler settings","properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["Вы можете протестировать и выбрать оптимальную настройку самостоятельно. Следующая таблица предназначена для справки.\n\n| model            | steps | cfg |\n|---------------------|---------------|---------------|\n| fp8_e4m3fn（Qwen team's suggestion）             | 40                | 2.5               \n| fp8_e4m3fn             | 20                | 2.5               |\n| fp8_e4m3fn + 8steps LoRA    | 8               | 2.5               |\n| fp8_e4m3fn + 4steps LoRA    | 4               | 1.0               |\n| GGUF             | 20                | 2.5               |\n| GGUF + 8steps LoRA    | 8               | 2.5               |\n| GGUF + 4steps LoRA    | 4               | 1.0               |\n| distill fp8_e4m3fn   | 10               | 1.0              |"],"color":"#432","bgcolor":"#653"},{"id":60,"type":"SaveImage","pos":[1430,60],"size":[425.7610168457031,521.3400268554688],"flags":{},"order":21,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"images","name":"images","type":"IMAGE","link":110},{"localized_nam